hat the condition for ECM emission is satisfied\nwithin areas of the corona containing large magnetic fields, such as the core\nof a large active region. Therefore, ECM could be a possible emission mechanism\nfor high-frequency radio and microwave bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Apr 2016 19:14:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-19"}
