merge from chaos since the best test\nfor a stew is its taste. Many long standing puzzles seem to have been resolved\nusing different techniques. The various explanations need to stand the test of\ntime before acceptance; but then unexpected outcomes set in and new puzzles\nemerge. As real analysis and limits tell us: We are getting Closer and Closer;\nYet it seems we are still Far Far Away...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Apr 2016 14:07:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2016 11:55:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 May 2016 03:29:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 31 May 2016 09:34:38 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 2 Mar 2018 02:05:56 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Wed, 8 May 2019 06:57:29 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 05:01:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
